metadata.name: Smiley's Smiles
metadata.description:
Smiley's smiles are the sun,  
A source of joy to everyone.  
His happiness radiates around,  
A warmth that can't be found.  
He laughs and twinkles in delight,  
A sparkle of life that's oh so bright.  
His infectious joy is a spark,  
That brings laughter in the dark.  
Smiley's smiles can light up a room,  
Like the shimmering light of the moon.  
His happy spirit is contagious,  
An endless joy that's so precious.
